Online todolist with terminal, browser and app interface

-- server
typescript

data:
    Shortterm list
    longterm list

Rest:
    GET     list
    POST    addShortterm(item: string)
    POST    addLongterm(item: string)
    DELETE  shortterm(index: int)
    DELETE  longterm(index: int)

-- browser and app
Angular2

list shortterm and longterm lists, allow for delete and add

-- terminal
typescript

cmds:
    todo ls
    todo ls -s
    todo ls -l
    todo add -s [string]
    todo add -l [string]
    todo delete -s [number]
    todo delete -l [number]
